source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06301_000005_NOPHICA<tab>At last, the time is come!
TEXT_VOICEMAN_06301_000030_MENPHINA<tab>Come bathe in the moon's tender glow!
TEXT_VOICEMAN_06301_000040_MENPHINA<tab>Our dreams may yet become reality. Thank you.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06301_000040_MENPHINA<tab>Merci infiniment. Nous voilà encore un peu plus proches de notre idéal...
